i18nspector (0.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Summary of tag changes:
    + Added:
      - arithmetic-error-in-plural-forms
      - arithmetic-error-in-unused-plural-forms
      - codomain-error-in-plural-forms
      - codomain-error-in-unused-plural-forms

